article_metadata.description: A searing review of Medi-Cal managed care provider directories released Tuesday by the California State Auditor found numerous inaccuracies ranging from incorrect phone numbers of doctors to listings of providers who no longer were participating in the health plans.
article_metadata.title: State auditor issues stinging review of Medi-Cal plans: Anthem Blue Cross in Fresno County gets worst grade | Fresno Bee
